summary:
An internationally experienced professional with background in Corporate Communications, Public Relations and Government Affairs.

Academic background in Political Sciences and International Relations with a strong passion for Diplomacy and Public affairs. Experience with working at the Embassy of Cyprus as a Public Relations Specialist, at Marcus Evans as a Marketing Executive, Communications and Branding Specialist at Boeing and currently appointed as a Media Relations Manager at CANSO.

Having lived, worked and studied in 5 countries and fluent in four languages, Angy has a global background and can thus bring an international approach to any position. Moreover the professional experience in both the public and private sector gave Angy a whole rounded education that makes her a flexible and adaptable young professional.
